## The Culturecode Manifesto License

This license governs the use and distribution of **The Culturecode Manifesto**.

In alignment with our belief in fostering critical thought, open dialogue, and
the free exchange of ideas, we choose a highly permissive license for this
foundational document. We encourage its broad sharing, thoughtful discussion,
and respectful adaptation, provided the spirit of its origins is acknowledged.

